00:57:39.000 --> 00:57:43.958
<i>Why do I have this strong feeling?</i>

741
00:57:44.083 --> 00:57:49.208
<i>That my whole world is you</i>

742
00:57:49.291 --> 00:57:51.708
<i>My whole world is you</i>

743
00:57:51.791 --> 00:57:56.583
<i>Without you. will my heart</i>
<i>Ever beat again?</i>

744
00:57:56.875 --> 00:58:00.875
<i>I keep asking myself that question</i>

745
00:58:01.750 --> 00:58:06.875
<i>Will you make all my pain vanish?</i>

746
00:58:07.125 --> 00:58:10.583
<i>That fills me with fear</i>

747
00:58:13.416 --> 00:58:18.375
<i>If I were to fall in love with you</i>

748
00:58:18.541 --> 00:58:23.625
<i>If I were to fall in love with you</i>

749
00:58:23.708 --> 00:58:28.708
<i>If I were to fall in love with you</i>

750
00:58:29.000 --> 00:58:34.125
<i>Love will undo my life</i>

751
00:58:36.166 --> 00:58:38.000
5000 likes in ten minutes!

752
00:58:38.750 --> 00:58:41.458
Is this for real?
Look at the comments.

753
00:58:41.916 --> 00:58:43.458
"When are you guys coming
with the video?

754
00:58:43.625 --> 00:58:45.500
"Please come soon. soon. soon."

755
00:58:46.125 --> 00:58:48.625
I have a solid concept!

756
00:58:48.875 --> 00:58:50.916
Road trip. Goa.

757
00:58:51.541 --> 00:58:52.916
Shooting while we travel.

758
00:58:53.208 --> 00:58:54.291
Where's the money?

759
00:58:55.500 --> 00:58:56.958
KV hasn't completed his master's yet.

760
00:59:02.750 --> 00:59:04.000
That's right.

761
00:59:04.666 --> 00:59:05.500
What?

762
00:59:14.750 --> 00:59:19.583
<i>If I were to fall in love with you</i>

763
00:59:20.041 --> 00:59:25.041
<i>Love will undo my life</i>

764
00:59:25.208 --> 00:59:29.916
<i>If I were to fall in love with you</i>

765
00:59:30.291 --> 00:59:37.291
<i>That love will know no bounds</i>

766
00:59:41.958 --> 00:59:42.791
Go.

767
00:59:45.833 --> 00:59:48.333
<i>Love will know no bounds</i>

768
01:00:19.000 --> 01:00:19.875
Who was he?

769
01:00:21.125 --> 01:00:21.958
Is he a friend?

770
01:00:23.041 --> 01:00:25.583
Is something going on?
You can tell me. I'm your mother.

771
01:00:26.250 --> 01:00:27.291
I don't know. Mom.

772
01:00:27.708 --> 01:00:30.458
Why don't you understand?

773
01:00:33.083 --> 01:00:35.291
Don't be so naive. my dear.

774
01:00:36.250 --> 01:00:39.375
Boys like him seduce innocent girls.

775
01:00:39.458 --> 01:00:41.416
When the high wears off.
they just leave.

776
01:00:43.833 --> 01:00:45.291
Did you tell him about Mahesh?

777
01:00:47.666 --> 01:00:50.041
I hope he doesn't think he can
take advantage of you.

778
01:00:53.500 --> 01:00:56.666
You've been let down badly once. my dear.

779
01:00:58.500 --> 01:01:01.333
You liked that boy earlier.
but he dumped you.

780
01:01:01.666 --> 01:01:04.291
It took us months to get you
out of your room.

781
01:01:05.041 --> 01:01:07.166
We also suffered with you.

782
01:01:08.833 --> 01:01:12.416
When their children suffer.
parents often slip into depression.

783
01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:17.125
Parents hate to see
their children with sad faces.

784
01:01:17.791 --> 01:01:20.750
We asked ourselves where we went wrong.

785
01:01:20.833 --> 01:01:24.791
You spent days crying.
but we wept for you too.

786
01:01:25.541 --> 01:01:26.833
People would make fun of us.

787
01:01:27.125 --> 01:01:28.833
These things happen.

788
01:01:28.916 --> 01:01:32.583
The doctor. our relatives.
everyone would say.

789
01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:35.708
"This happens in love."

790
01:01:36.166 --> 01:01:37.083
You listening?

791
01:01:37.750 --> 01:01:39.625
I've been ranting on like
some madwoman.

792
01:01:41.041 --> 01:01:43.083
Vaani. what is it?

793
01:01:44.041 --> 01:01:46.500
Vaani. What's wrong? Vaani!

794
01:02:02.875 --> 01:02:05.083
Vaani. it's okay. Please get up.

795
01:02:16.666 --> 01:02:19.125
Sometimes. intense stress
can trigger this reaction.

796
01:02:19.541 --> 01:02:20.791
But it's nothing serious.

797
01:02:21.916 --> 01:02:25.416
A few blood tests and two to three hours
of observation are all we require.

798
01:02:25.500 --> 01:02:27.041
And you can take her home by morning.

799
01:02:27.708 --> 01:02:30.958
Just to be on the safer side.
take her to a neurologist.

800
01:02:31.458 --> 01:02:33.791
Dr. Khyati. Get an appointment with her.

801
01:02:33.875 --> 01:02:36.500
- Where do I book an appointment. Doctor?
- At the reception.

802
01:02:36.875 --> 01:02:37.916
- Thank you.
- Thank you. Sir.

803
01:02:38.333 --> 01:02:39.208
Listen.

804
01:02:48.125 --> 01:02:49.125
You can go in.

805
01:03:01.958 --> 01:03:02.833
Listen.

806
01:03:04.708 --> 01:03:06.416
She's suffered a lot.

807
01:03:07.958 --> 01:03:09.000
She's a very simple girl.

808
01:03:10.583 --> 01:03:11.791
Will you marry her?

809
01:03:15.416 --> 01:03:17.041
Will you marry her?

810
01:03:19.583 --> 01:03:21.583
No? Answer me.

811
01:03:22.041 --> 01:03:22.916
Leave her.

812
01:03:23.916 --> 01:03:25.458
You'll find many other girls.

813
01:03:27.958 --> 01:03:29.416
My daughter is not a pastime.

814
01:03:31.125 --> 01:03:34.000
- If something happens to her--
- Geeta! What's this nonsense?

815
01:03:34.125 --> 01:03:35.750
You crazy? Be quiet!

816
01:03:36.666 --> 01:03:37.500
Quiet!

817
01:03:49.666 --> 01:03:51.375
Hold it for a while.

818
01:04:10.708 --> 01:04:11.791
Let's get married.

819
01:04:17.000 --> 01:04:17.958
What?

820
01:04:24.125 --> 01:04:25.958
Marriage. You and me.

821
01:04:27.875 --> 01:04:29.583
Because I fainted?

822
01:04:31.666 --> 01:04:33.791
Krish. do you even know
the meaning of marriage?

823
01:04:35.875 --> 01:04:37.125
- Attended any weddings?
- Oh. hello!

824
01:04:37.833 --> 01:04:40.083
I've performed at 40 weddings.
I know the routine.

825
01:04:43.125 --> 01:04:44.250
It's no big deal.

826
01:04:45.166 --> 01:04:47.458
One priest. two garlands.
seven rounds.

827
01:04:47.833 --> 01:04:50.208
A hundred guests will give cash
for good luck.

828
01:04:50.291 --> 01:04:53.166
- They eat. drink. and just leave.
- Quiet! Stop it!

829
01:04:55.375 --> 01:04:56.625
You don't know anything.

830
01:04:58.166 --> 01:05:02.875
You don't know if you love me.
or what we mean to each other.

831
01:05:02.958 --> 01:05:05.416
But you somehow decided to marry me.

832
01:05:08.458 --> 01:05:09.666
Did my mom say something?

833
01:05:18.541 --> 01:05:20.791
Krish. I've made this mistake before.

834
01:05:22.625 --> 01:05:25.916
For someone's present.
I sacrificed my future.

835
01:05:27.041 --> 01:05:28.375
Even though my heart wasn't ready.

836
01:05:28.666 --> 01:05:31.625
I kept convincing myself
that his dreams were my dreams.

837
01:05:33.041 --> 01:05:35.000
And my dreams didn't matter.

838
01:05:40.541 --> 01:05:41.708
Don't do it.

839
01:05:44.750 --> 01:05:45.708
Please.

840
01:05:48.708 --> 01:05:51.500
I'll get married someday.
I won't have any regrets.

841
01:05:51.583 --> 01:05:53.791
But you know what I'll regret?

842
01:05:56.791 --> 01:05:58.750
That you didn't become a superstar.

843
01:06:01.375 --> 01:06:03.541
Go get what you've always wanted.

844
01:06:06.750 --> 01:06:08.291
Go. Shoot that video.

845
01:06:19.750 --> 01:06:20.958
Take care. dear.

846
01:06:34.833 --> 01:06:40.083
<i>I fear falling in love</i>

847
01:06:40.666 --> 01:06:45.791
<i>I fear falling in love</i>

848
01:06:46.541 --> 01:06:52.208
<i>I dare not fall in love</i>

849
01:07:05.333 --> 01:07:06.791
- Is there trouble?
- Harry. wake up. Look!

850
01:07:07.500 --> 01:07:09.000
- Bro!
- Where did so many people come from?

851
01:07:09.083 --> 01:07:10.458
Guys. what is happening?

852
01:07:10.541 --> 01:07:11.791
- Who are all these people?
- What's the matter?

853
01:07:11.875 --> 01:07:14.916
We're here.
There's a big crowd outside the hotel.

854
01:07:15.000 --> 01:07:15.958
Krish. what are you doing?

855
01:07:16.958 --> 01:07:19.375
- Krish! Wait?
- Where are you going?

856
01:07:31.125 --> 01:07:33.083
Everyone's going on top?

857
01:07:33.583 --> 01:07:35.208
Cleo. aren't these people getting
too aggressive?

858
01:07:35.291 --> 01:07:36.291
Who are these people. KV?

859
01:07:36.375 --> 01:07:38.833
I don't understand what's going on.

860
01:07:38.916 --> 01:07:40.958
Over 20.000 organic reels are ready.

861
01:07:41.041 --> 01:07:42.791
Got 50.000 shares already.

862
01:07:43.041 --> 01:07:44.125
They're all over Spotify.

863
01:07:44.208 --> 01:07:46.708
Audio is number four on YouTube.
not even a video. We're trending!

864
01:07:47.000 --> 01:07:48.375
Collection rate is on fire.

865
01:07:50.166 --> 01:07:51.250
I can't look past the crowd. man!

866
01:07:54.875 --> 01:07:56.041
You're a star now.

867
01:07:58.250 --> 01:07:59.125
Oh. yes!

868
01:07:59.375 --> 01:08:02.500
Look at that. Huge crowd.

869
01:08:02.583 --> 01:08:03.708
They're all your fans.

870
01:08:04.625 --> 01:08:06.708
They've been waiting all day
to see you.

871
01:08:07.125 --> 01:08:08.750
Your song's a killer.

872
01:08:08.958 --> 01:08:10.750
The Internet is on fire!

873
01:08:10.833 --> 01:08:12.041
You can't believe it?

874
01:08:12.541 --> 01:08:13.375
One second.

875
01:08:15.416 --> 01:08:18.791
OMG. he's Krish Kapoor!

876
01:08:20.916 --> 01:08:23.791
And we are the Josh Crew.

877
01:08:25.083 --> 01:08:27.791
Josh!

878
01:08:34.041 --> 01:08:35.041
What is this?

879
01:08:35.958 --> 01:08:37.750
This is crazy. man.

880
01:08:42.708 --> 01:08:43.708
What is he doing here?

881
01:08:58.916 --> 01:09:00.875
Are you suffering from
a head injury?

882
01:09:01.458 --> 01:09:02.333
No.

883
01:09:02.958 --> 01:09:04.166
No. Come.

884
01:09:06.666 --> 01:09:09.250
Are you on any kind of medication?

885
01:09:09.916 --> 01:09:12.041
Pills. supplements. anything?

886
01:09:12.416 --> 01:09:16.083
My dad gives me flaxseed oil.
calcium. and iron.

887
01:09:16.791 --> 01:09:19.750
But I don't take it regularly
because I keep forgetting to take it.

888
01:09:19.833 --> 01:09:20.708
Okay.

889
01:09:23.375 --> 01:09:24.791
- Let's try a test.
- Yeah.

890
01:09:24.875 --> 01:09:26.541
- Routine. Okay?
- Okay.

891
01:09:27.041 --> 01:09:31.000
Please remember
what I'm going to say. Okay?

892
01:09:32.041 --> 01:09:35.916
Vijay Sharma. 33 M.G. Road. Bangalore.

893
01:09:36.291 --> 01:09:37.958
Can you repeat that after me. please?

894
01:09:38.041 --> 01:09:39.666
Yes. Vijay Sharma.

895
01:09:39.750 --> 01:09:41.583
- Yes.
- 33…

896
01:09:42.000 --> 01:09:44.125
Vijay Sharma. 33. M.G. Road. Bangalore.

897
01:09:45.791 --> 01:09:46.791
What are you doing?

898
01:09:47.375 --> 01:09:48.416
I keep on…

899
01:09:48.500 --> 01:09:50.250
I forget things.

900
01:09:50.333 --> 01:09:52.125
That's why I write everything in my diary.

901
01:09:52.583 --> 01:09:54.458
Do you always do that?

902
01:09:56.458 --> 01:09:57.666
What's today's date?

903
01:10:03.250 --> 01:10:04.125
Sorry.

904
01:10:06.541 --> 01:10:09.500
I don't remember dates.
I don't know.

905
01:10:10.708 --> 01:10:14.583
It's the 21st February. 2025.

906
01:10:15.416 --> 01:10:16.375
Will you remember that?

907
01:10:18.083 --> 01:10:18.916
Oh.

908
01:10:19.916 --> 01:10:21.291
Do you have any siblings?

909
01:10:23.541 --> 01:10:24.458
I have a brother.

910
01:10:25.458 --> 01:10:26.375
How old is he?

911
01:10:27.750 --> 01:10:28.750
He's 12.

912
01:10:31.625 --> 01:10:33.333
Sorry. I think…

913
01:10:36.416 --> 01:10:37.750
Actually. he's 13.

914
01:10:41.208 --> 01:10:43.166
I'm confused. I'm bad with
numbers. also.

915
01:10:44.916 --> 01:10:47.625
Do you remember the name
and address I just said?

916
01:10:53.916 --> 01:10:57.500
Was it M.G. Road? S.V. Road?
Or Linking Road?

917
01:11:06.208 --> 01:11:07.083
I…

918
01:11:09.000 --> 01:11:11.708
I was a little distracted.
Could you repeat the address?

919
01:11:14.250 --> 01:11:16.000
You must remember today's date?

920
01:11:21.958 --> 01:11:22.833
No.

921
01:11:28.916 --> 01:11:30.708
Did anyone accompany you here?

922
01:11:31.458 --> 01:11:34.500
Family or friend?

923
01:11:36.041 --> 01:11:36.916
No.

924
01:11:38.666 --> 01:11:39.541
Why?

925
01:11:40.791 --> 01:11:41.666
Is there a problem?

926
01:11:46.083 --> 01:11:50.375
Vaani. your blood reports
don't show any deficiency.

927
01:11:51.125 --> 01:11:56.291
We have scanned your brain. Neuroimaging.

928
01:11:56.375 --> 01:11:57.291
Yeah.

929
01:11:57.958 --> 01:12:00.833
There were no signs of a stroke.

930
01:12:02.125 --> 01:12:03.500
But there's something else.

931
01:12:07.208 --> 01:12:11.250
The results are consistent
with Alzheimer's disease.

932
01:12:15.583 --> 01:12:17.250
Sorry. Alzheimer's?

933
01:12:17.958 --> 01:12:18.833
Yes. Vaani.

934
01:12:20.500 --> 01:12:22.250
Your memory is deteriorating.

935
01:12:23.291 --> 01:12:26.583
Normally. it affects older people.

936
01:12:26.666 --> 01:12:31.125
But if we find it occurring before 65.

937
01:12:31.208 --> 01:12:33.458
it's called early-onset Alzheimer's.

938
01:12:33.541 --> 01:12:34.416
There's like a…

939
01:12:35.791 --> 01:12:38.250
0.4% chance of it happening.

940
01:12:39.000 --> 01:12:42.458
A Chinese boy of 17 was diagnosed with it.

941
01:12:42.875 --> 01:12:48.500
His… symptoms started like yours.

942
01:12:52.375 --> 01:12:53.916
So what does it mean?

943
01:12:55.750 --> 01:12:56.750
What will happen?

944
01:13:01.875 --> 01:13:02.791
<i>Vaani.</i>

945
01:13:03.916 --> 01:13:06.125
<i>you'll have to inform everyone.</i>

946
01:13:07.333 --> 01:13:10.041
Because you can't fight this alone.

947
01:13:11.208 --> 01:13:14.041
<i>You're already forgetting small details.</i>

948
01:13:15.791 --> 01:13:16.791
<i>And slowly. for you.</i>

949
01:13:17.416 --> 01:13:20.375
remembering events and incidents
will become difficult.

950
01:13:22.875 --> 01:13:26.291
Later. you'll forget people
who are dear to you.

951
01:13:27.291 --> 01:13:30.041
<i>Your family. your friends.</i>

952
01:13:31.250 --> 01:13:32.125
<i>your love.</i>

953
01:13:35.750 --> 01:13:36.583
Vaani!

954
01:13:42.708 --> 01:13:44.125
Why weren't you taking my calls?

955
01:13:46.791 --> 01:13:47.833
You've forgotten about me.

956
01:13:50.500 --> 01:13:52.750
I was away for only two days.
and you stopped taking my calls.

957
01:13:55.666 --> 01:13:57.583
- Krish. I have something to tell you.
- First. see this.

958
01:13:58.750 --> 01:13:59.666
500 people. Vaani.

959
01:14:00.458 --> 01:14:01.333
They were crying out my name!

960
01:14:04.083 --> 01:14:05.791
- Krish. I--
- That Vinit.

961
01:14:06.041 --> 01:14:07.125
the YMX Records guy.

962
01:14:07.208 --> 01:14:09.166
came round to sign me up.

963
01:14:10.500 --> 01:14:12.458
No music video.
Straight to the Delhi Music Festival.

964
01:14:12.541 --> 01:14:15.583
Shows. album deals. radio spots.

965
01:14:16.000 --> 01:14:18.083
But the main thing.
I'll get full credit. Vaani.

966
01:14:18.541 --> 01:14:20.333
My name will be everywhere.
Vaani. it'll be up there.

967
01:14:23.166 --> 01:14:25.916
Whatever I wanted in life was once
within my grasp.

968
01:14:26.000 --> 01:14:27.375
but I wasn't happy. Do you know why?

969
01:14:30.541 --> 01:14:31.958
Because you weren't there.

970
01:14:36.000 --> 01:14:36.916
- Krish--
- Vaani.

971
01:14:37.166 --> 01:14:40.333
I was a good singer.
but not a good person. I was a fool.

972
01:14:42.291 --> 01:14:44.625
Full of rage.
Mad at the world.

973
01:14:47.541 --> 01:14:48.416
Now everyone…

974
01:14:50.875 --> 01:14:54.416
believes in my talent. Vaani.
But you accepted my flaws.

975
01:14:56.916 --> 01:14:58.708
You told me to get
what I've always wanted.

976
01:14:58.791 --> 01:14:59.958
So I've come to you.

977
01:15:01.208 --> 01:15:02.125
And I'm not letting you go.

978
01:15:04.708 --> 01:15:06.083
Not now. not ever.

979
01:15:09.166 --> 01:15:10.083
Come.

980
01:15:10.250 --> 01:15:11.500
- Come with me.
- Where?

981
01:15:11.958 --> 01:15:12.916
Let's go.

982
01:15:14.000 --> 01:15:15.000
Let's go. let's go. let's go.

983
01:15:28.541 --> 01:15:29.875
That's where I want to reach. Vaani.

984
01:15:32.416 --> 01:15:33.333
But not alone.

985
01:15:35.791 --> 01:15:36.666
with you.

986
01:15:38.583 --> 01:15:40.416
The whole world
will remember my name.

987
01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:44.291
They'll all shout.
"Krish Kapoor. we love you.

988
01:15:45.333 --> 01:15:46.750
We love you. Krish Kapoor.

989
01:15:46.833 --> 01:15:50.333
Krish Kapoor. we love you.
We love you. Krish Kapoor!"

990
01:15:56.500 --> 01:15:57.916
But I love you. Vaani Batra.

991
01:15:59.166 --> 01:16:01.791
I love you forever.

992
01:16:02.708 --> 01:16:03.583
and ever.

993
01:16:04.291 --> 01:16:06.666
and ever. and ever.

994
01:16:20.958 --> 01:16:24.708
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

995
01:16:25.708 --> 01:16:29.500
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

996
01:16:29.583 --> 01:16:33.166
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

997
01:16:44.875 --> 01:16:48.958
What about your test. my dear?
Did you get the report?

998
01:16:50.416 --> 01:16:51.250
Vaani.

999
01:16:52.791 --> 01:16:53.625
Vaani?

1000
01:16:55.291 --> 01:16:56.250
I forgot about it. Dad.

1001
01:16:58.375 --> 01:17:00.208
You're all grown up.
but you're so forgetful.

1002
01:17:00.500 --> 01:17:02.708
One day. you're going to forget your dad!

1003
01:17:04.375 --> 01:17:08.000
<i>Vaani. you'll have to inform</i>
<i>your family and friends.</i>

1004
01:17:09.208 --> 01:17:12.541
<i>Your symptoms will escalate quickly.</i>

1005
01:17:13.041 --> 01:17:14.958
You'll get confused about time.

1006
01:17:16.500 --> 01:17:20.625
<i>The past will seem like</i>
<i>the present to you.</i>

1007
01:17:21.583 --> 01:17:26.791
You could get emotionally upset by this
confusion between the past and present.

1008
01:17:28.083 --> 01:17:29.416
<i>You could get very angry.</i>

1009
01:17:30.583 --> 01:17:33.833
<i>You can have violent episodes.</i>

1010
01:17:34.541 --> 01:17:39.375
Medicine and treatment
can slow down this disease.

1011
01:17:41.041 --> 01:17:42.041
but they cannot cure it.

1012
01:17:43.208 --> 01:17:45.458
Vaani! Vaani. please come.

1013
01:17:46.416 --> 01:17:47.458
Come. Let's celebrate.

1014
01:17:48.583 --> 01:17:50.083
- Please.
- Vaani. there you are!

1015
01:17:50.166 --> 01:17:52.083
Come. let me introduce you to someone.

1016
01:17:53.416 --> 01:17:54.625
Mr. Mahesh Iyer.

1017
01:17:56.166 --> 01:18:00.208
Your college friend and now
our partner. investor.

1018
01:18:01.166 --> 01:18:02.166
<i>I won't be coming. Vaani.</i>

1019
01:18:02.958 --> 01:18:05.625
{\an8}<i>I don't want to get married.</i>
<i>Vaani. I have…</i>

1020
01:18:06.125 --> 01:18:07.166
<i>I've met someone else.</i>

1021
01:18:07.750 --> 01:18:09.250
Vaani! My dear!

1022
01:18:11.500 --> 01:18:12.541
So good to see you. Vans.

1023
01:18:16.416 --> 01:18:17.250
Look at you!

1024
01:18:18.666 --> 01:18:21.541
You're doing so well.
you're looking great.

1025
01:18:23.458 --> 01:18:26.208
Since we released your podcast.
it's been like a miracle.

1026
01:18:26.541 --> 01:18:28.958
Their company. Soulmates.
and their parent company.

1027
01:18:29.041 --> 01:18:31.208
the Grover family.
are joining hands with us.

1028
01:18:31.708 --> 01:18:35.166
You know. Vaani. since you joined us.
we've had such good luck.

1029
01:18:35.583 --> 01:18:36.416
Touchwood.

1030
01:18:37.125 --> 01:18:37.958
Anyway. guys.

1031
01:18:38.291 --> 01:18:40.458
- see you at the party tomorrow.
- Oh. yes.

1032
01:18:43.791 --> 01:18:45.041
I hope you're coming.

1033
01:18:45.708 --> 01:18:46.708
Of course. she'll be there.

1034
01:18:48.000 --> 01:18:48.833
Great.

1035
01:18:51.583 --> 01:18:53.000
I don't know when I'm going
to come back.

1036
01:18:56.625 --> 01:18:58.458
Delhi. Shillong. then Guwahati.

1037
01:18:59.000 --> 01:19:01.083
Some college events.
some corporate shows.

1038
01:19:01.541 --> 01:19:04.125
KV said we have to promote the song
in the northern belt of India!

1039
01:19:05.250 --> 01:19:07.375
Malls. radio spots.

1040
01:19:09.083 --> 01:19:10.125
We must be heard in small towns. too.

1041
01:19:11.291 --> 01:19:13.750
Maybe even a show in Ghaziabad.
Can you imagine?

1042
01:19:16.416 --> 01:19:17.458
I'm quitting my job.

1043
01:19:20.000 --> 01:19:20.875
Why? Anything wrong?

1044
01:19:21.458 --> 01:19:22.541
It was going well.

1045
01:19:24.666 --> 01:19:26.083
Nothing's happening.
That's just the problem.

1046
01:19:27.541 --> 01:19:29.458
We keep guessing
when it comes to interviews.

1047
01:19:29.541 --> 01:19:30.666
Try a rapid-fire round.

1048
01:19:31.041 --> 01:19:34.833
Drop your questions because celebs
want you to ask their questions.

1049
01:19:35.750 --> 01:19:37.250
This is not what I wanted to do.
This is like…

1050
01:19:37.333 --> 01:19:39.083
It's not journalism.
And I'm sick of it.

1051
01:19:40.208 --> 01:19:41.208
Vaani. what are you doing?

1052
01:19:43.250 --> 01:19:45.000
You'll miss your flight.
You packed?

1053
01:19:46.208 --> 01:19:47.041
I'm doing it.

1054
01:19:47.833 --> 01:19:49.666
Doing things at the last minute…
irresponsible.

1055
01:19:50.458 --> 01:19:51.708
Vaani. the bag is already packed.

1056
01:19:55.250 --> 01:19:56.458
We packed it together.

1057
01:20:11.833 --> 01:20:16.208
There was no traffic 20 minutes ago.
Now it's all red!

1058
01:20:16.291 --> 01:20:18.083
We could miss the flight
on our first tour.

1059
01:20:18.166 --> 01:20:20.708
- Come on. guys.
- We don't have a chartered flight. right?

1060
01:20:23.166 --> 01:20:24.250
Is everything okay. Vaani?

1061
01:20:25.416 --> 01:20:26.250
I'm fine.

1062
01:20:29.916 --> 01:20:32.166
You said how excited
you were about the tour.

1063
01:20:35.958 --> 01:20:38.333
I just got a-- got a bit confused.

1064
01:20:48.583 --> 01:20:49.500
Go!

1065
01:20:55.166 --> 01:20:56.041
Go!

1066
01:21:18.375 --> 01:21:19.500
Ma'am. could I please have your name?

1067
01:21:21.916 --> 01:21:22.875
Ma'am. your name?

1068
01:21:24.125 --> 01:21:25.000
Excuse me. ma'am.

1069
01:21:28.250 --> 01:21:29.208
Are you with someone. ma'am?

1070
01:21:30.708 --> 01:21:31.541
Vaani.

1071
01:21:34.250 --> 01:21:35.166
Why are you standing here?

1072
01:21:37.291 --> 01:21:38.125
Why did you stop her?

1073
01:21:38.583 --> 01:21:40.416
She didn't tell me her name.

1074
01:21:40.833 --> 01:21:41.708
Sorry. sir.

1075
01:21:44.208 --> 01:21:45.208
I'm sorry for this.

1076
01:21:46.708 --> 01:21:49.208
Come. Welcome to Soulmates!

1077
01:22:02.250 --> 01:22:03.083
Here you go.

1078
01:22:04.166 --> 01:22:05.000
Still not drinking?

1079
01:22:08.083 --> 01:22:09.041
Come on. Vans.

1080
01:22:10.375 --> 01:22:11.583
Remember how you were at college?

1081
01:22:13.791 --> 01:22:18.083
You used to be scared of crowds.
You were a simple. sober person.

1082
01:22:19.250 --> 01:22:20.083
But now look at you!

1083
01:22:21.791 --> 01:22:22.666
Beautiful.

1084
01:22:23.375 --> 01:22:24.291
glamorous.

1085
01:22:25.000 --> 01:22:25.875
hot.

1086
01:22:26.875 --> 01:22:27.875
Hot. Vaani.

1087
01:22:29.041 --> 01:22:32.291
<i>You know. I had no need of</i>
<i>this hippie company.</i>

1088
01:22:34.625 --> 01:22:38.208
<i>I don't care about Buzzlist or Neha.</i>

1089
01:22:40.041 --> 01:22:42.750
I bought it for you.

1090
01:22:48.375 --> 01:22:53.125
If you do what I say.
you'll be good.

1091
01:22:53.208 --> 01:22:54.666
Forget about writing.

1092
01:22:56.625 --> 01:23:00.041
I can remember all the good times.

1093
01:23:02.500 --> 01:23:06.416
I've missed you a lot. Vans.

1094
01:23:07.416 --> 01:23:10.416
I remember everything.

1095
01:23:13.083 --> 01:23:14.000
How's everyone at home?

1096
01:23:18.000 --> 01:23:18.833
Meaning?

1097
01:23:20.333 --> 01:23:24.458
I mean. your parents
and that brother of yours.

1098
01:23:25.833 --> 01:23:26.875
Do they know we were meeting today?

1099
01:23:32.166 --> 01:23:33.791
They've always wanted us
to be together.

1100
01:23:34.541 --> 01:23:35.833
Did they want us to meet again?

1101
01:23:38.666 --> 01:23:39.875
Did you tell them about me?

1102
01:23:44.708 --> 01:23:46.125
Aren't we getting married?

1103
01:23:56.125 --> 01:23:57.000
Getting married?

1104
01:23:58.791 --> 01:23:59.625
Us?

1105
01:24:09.166 --> 01:24:10.416
Didn't you propose?

1106
01:24:12.625 --> 01:24:13.625
Why are you smiling now?

1107
01:24:15.041 --> 01:24:16.458
Did your parents say anything?

1108
01:24:18.083 --> 01:24:19.708
Vaani. what have my parents
got to do with it?

1109
01:24:19.791 --> 01:24:20.666
Did they?

1110
01:24:20.750 --> 01:24:21.833
Vaani. everyone's staring at us.
Let's talk later.

1111
01:24:21.916 --> 01:24:23.875
- Why later?
- Let's talk later.

1112
01:24:23.958 --> 01:24:25.625
Why must we talk later. Mahesh?

1113
01:24:27.750 --> 01:24:29.541
Why can't we talk right now?

1114
01:24:31.125 --> 01:24:33.208
Why can't we be together?
Why not?

1115
01:24:33.291 --> 01:24:34.833
Vaani. why are you creating a scene?

1116
01:24:35.541 --> 01:24:39.375
- As if you didn't know--
- What are you playing at?

1117
01:24:39.458 --> 01:24:40.291
Mahesh!

1118
01:24:50.666 --> 01:24:52.291
What's happening here?
Who is she?

1119
01:24:53.375 --> 01:24:54.208
No one. babe.

1120
01:24:54.958 --> 01:24:57.000
Just an employee. She's going
to lose her job after the merger.

1121
01:24:57.083 --> 01:24:58.500
so she's creating a scene.

1122
01:24:58.916 --> 01:25:01.375
But don't worry.
I'll ask security to deal with her.

1123
01:25:01.916 --> 01:25:02.833
Just relax. Okay.

1124
01:25:03.208 --> 01:25:04.791
Has anybody called the security?

1125
01:25:18.750 --> 01:25:19.583
Ma'am.

1126
01:25:20.083 --> 01:25:21.166
Ma'am. you'll have to come with me.

1127
01:25:22.083 --> 01:25:22.916
Ma'am.

1128
01:25:25.916 --> 01:25:26.750
Are you okay?

1129
01:25:28.416 --> 01:25:29.333
Can I help you. ma'am?

1130
01:25:30.833 --> 01:25:31.708
Ma'am.

1131
01:25:31.916 --> 01:25:32.750
Ma'am.

1132
01:26:08.208 --> 01:26:09.125
Vaani. where are you?

1133
01:26:09.208 --> 01:26:10.375
- Thank you.
- Thank you. ma'am.

1134
01:26:12.041 --> 01:26:12.916
Krish!

1135
01:26:14.875 --> 01:26:15.708
What happened?

1136
01:26:17.750 --> 01:26:18.625
What is it. Krish?

1137
01:26:26.666 --> 01:26:30.500
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1138
01:26:30.583 --> 01:26:33.833
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1139
01:26:33.916 --> 01:26:38.916
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1140
01:27:34.875 --> 01:27:37.625
The machine is out of order
like KV's brain.

1141
01:27:39.708 --> 01:27:42.083
Try smacking him on the head.

1142
01:27:47.083 --> 01:27:48.125
A good shot.

1143
01:27:49.291 --> 01:27:51.833
You have to improve your posture.

1144
01:27:54.000 --> 01:27:54.875
Okay.

1145
01:27:55.000 --> 01:27:57.500
Elbow right angle.
Let the ball get closer.

1146
01:27:57.708 --> 01:27:59.583
Strike with your front foot.
not the back foot.

1147
01:27:59.708 --> 01:28:01.583
When the ball comes at you.
you swing.

1148
01:28:01.750 --> 01:28:04.375
Okay. don't worry. I'm right here.

1149
01:28:09.500 --> 01:28:10.583
So you know now.

1150
01:28:14.208 --> 01:28:16.583
- Say something. Krish.
- Why didn't you tell me?

1151
01:28:17.791 --> 01:28:20.708
You thought no one would find out
about your condition?

1152
01:28:20.791 --> 01:28:22.125
Listen to me and just go.

1153
01:28:23.208 --> 01:28:24.208
Leave me alone.

1154
01:28:24.291 --> 01:28:26.458
- I don't want to listen to anything.
- There are lots of doctors.

1155
01:28:27.916 --> 01:28:31.791
There must be a cure. maybe in the US.
We'll get help somewhere.

1156
01:28:31.875 --> 01:28:34.500
- We'll find a way.
- I have Alzheimer's. Krish.

1157
01:28:38.291 --> 01:28:39.541
There's no cure for it.

1158
01:28:41.541 --> 01:28:45.500
Go anywhere you want to. Talk
to any doctor. and they'll all tell you

1159
01:28:46.166 --> 01:28:47.750
my memory is deteriorating.

1160
01:28:50.208 --> 01:28:54.333
Those moments we spent together
that taught me to live.

1161
01:28:54.416 --> 01:28:57.583
- those memories will disappear.
- But I'll be there.

1162
01:28:57.875 --> 01:28:59.416
Why don't you understand. Krish?

1163
01:29:00.833 --> 01:29:04.208
I won't remember who I am.
I won't remember about you.

1164
01:29:05.791 --> 01:29:07.833
I love you so much.

1165
01:29:09.166 --> 01:29:11.750
Your career.

1166
01:29:13.166 --> 01:29:14.125
your life.

1167
01:29:15.833 --> 01:29:17.666
I have no right over them.

1168
01:29:18.291 --> 01:29:20.458
- Or your future--
- To hell with my future. Vaani!

1169
01:29:24.750 --> 01:29:25.875
All I can know is the present.

1170
01:29:27.833 --> 01:29:28.666
this moment.

1171
01:29:31.541 --> 01:29:33.166
And in this moment. you're with me.

1172
01:29:37.416 --> 01:29:39.708
I love you right now. Vaani.

1173
01:29:42.333 --> 01:29:45.625
What's the worst that could happen?
You'll forget things.

1174
01:29:47.416 --> 01:29:48.625
We'll make new memories.

1175
01:29:51.333 --> 01:29:52.791
You'll forget again.
I'll make another.

1176
01:29:53.125 --> 01:29:55.458
Forget one memory. I'll make ten.

1177
01:29:55.833 --> 01:29:57.625
A hundred. A thousand.

1178
01:29:59.791 --> 01:30:00.958
Whatever happens.

1179
01:30:02.250 --> 01:30:03.250
I'm not letting you go.

1180
01:30:04.416 --> 01:30:06.750
Not now. not ever.

1181
01:30:07.208 --> 01:30:12.000
Forever and ever.
forever and ever. and ever.

1182
01:30:13.250 --> 01:30:17.166
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1183
01:30:17.250 --> 01:30:20.291
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1184
01:30:20.375 --> 01:30:23.000
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1185
01:30:27.750 --> 01:30:30.833
There'll be many rounds
of medicines and checkups.

1186
01:30:31.375 --> 01:30:34.375
But what we need is to set up
a daily routine now.

1187
01:30:35.125 --> 01:30:37.375
Wake up at the same time every day.

1188
01:30:37.750 --> 01:30:39.541
and go for a walk in the sunlight.

1189
01:30:40.000 --> 01:30:43.333
And above all.
don't let her get stressed.

1190
01:30:44.125 --> 01:30:47.583
If it's possible. take her
somewhere peaceful.

1191
01:30:48.000 --> 01:30:50.750
<i>it may be the countryside.</i>
<i>Or the mountains?</i>

1192
01:30:51.458 --> 01:30:53.500
<i>Away from the city bustle.</i>

1193
01:30:54.166 --> 01:30:57.416
Babbi. My cousin Babbi.

1194
01:30:57.750 --> 01:31:00.291
She has a house in Nainital.
I'll take her there.

1195
01:31:00.375 --> 01:31:01.375
No.

1196
01:31:02.291 --> 01:31:06.250
Rudransh has his exams soon.
I'll take her.

1197
01:31:06.333 --> 01:31:08.833
- And work?
- I'll retire.

1198
01:31:09.375 --> 01:31:11.125
She needs a mother more.
I'll take her.

1199
01:31:11.208 --> 01:31:12.583
Why must you be so stubborn?

1200
01:31:14.708 --> 01:31:16.208
She must have her medicines on time.

1201
01:31:16.291 --> 01:31:18.000
- You'll need a timetable.
- I will…

1202
01:31:18.083 --> 01:31:20.416
You can't handle it. I'll go.

1203
01:31:20.500 --> 01:31:23.875
- But I can.
- You look after Rudransh.

1204
01:31:25.041 --> 01:31:27.083
- I feel like crying…
- Now don't cry.

1205
01:31:31.166 --> 01:31:33.833
Dad. I won't take sides.
I'm on my own side.

1206
01:31:33.916 --> 01:31:36.625
- I know. my dear.
- Dad. let it drop.

1207
01:31:36.708 --> 01:31:37.541
Wait!

1208
01:31:37.666 --> 01:31:38.875
How could she just leave?

1209
01:31:38.958 --> 01:31:40.750
Please take care of Mom.

1210
01:31:41.208 --> 01:31:43.666
- Don't shout. I'll do.
- Send the girl alone.

1211
01:31:43.750 --> 01:31:45.708
Hold it. Don't talk.

1212
01:31:45.791 --> 01:31:46.958
- Here.
- What are you doing?

1213
01:31:47.125 --> 01:31:50.500
Our daughter is going to Alibaug
just for two months. Don't worry.

1214
01:31:51.458 --> 01:31:52.333
Take care.

1215
01:31:54.291 --> 01:31:55.458
Everything's going to be all right.

1216
01:32:01.250 --> 01:32:02.083
Leave.

1217
01:32:39.125 --> 01:32:42.583
<i>From the moment</i>

1218
01:32:43.125 --> 01:32:46.541
<i>I held your hand in mine</i>

1219
01:32:47.375 --> 01:32:50.958
<i>It feels like a restless river</i>

1220
01:32:51.500 --> 01:32:54.875
<i>Has found a calm shore</i>

1221
01:32:54.958 --> 01:33:00.250
<i>Even my restless wanderings</i>

1222
01:33:00.375 --> 01:33:03.083
<i>Have found peace in you</i>

1223
01:33:03.291 --> 01:33:08.625
<i>Every moment by your side</i>

1224
01:33:08.708 --> 01:33:11.875
<i>Weaves a new memory in me</i>

1225
01:33:12.416 --> 01:33:15.916
<i>- With you. each dawn feels new</i>
- Vaani!

1226
01:33:16.583 --> 01:33:20.000
<i>- With you. each evening is divine</i>
- Come on.

1227
01:33:20.083 --> 01:33:25.083
- No one is here.
<i>- Is this a world of dreams?</i>

1228
01:33:25.166 --> 01:33:28.541
<i>With you. it feels so real</i>

1229
01:33:29.083 --> 01:33:32.583
<i>With you. all seems right</i>

1230
01:33:33.291 --> 01:33:36.958
<i>With you. time stands still</i>

1231
01:33:37.458 --> 01:33:41.583
<i>With you. this moment is alive</i>

1232
01:33:41.916 --> 01:33:45.291
<i>With you. this moment is eternity</i>

1233
01:33:45.833 --> 01:33:49.500
<i>With you</i>

1234
01:33:54.833 --> 01:33:59.166
<i>This moment is eternity</i>

1235
01:34:05.000 --> 01:34:07.916
<i>When I met you</i>

1236
01:34:08.416 --> 01:34:13.083
{\an8}<i>You took away all my suffering</i>

1237
01:34:13.166 --> 01:34:15.958
<i>When I met you</i>

1238
01:34:16.666 --> 01:34:21.250
<i>You brought calm to my restless mind</i>

1239
01:34:21.333 --> 01:34:24.166
<i>What can I say?</i>

1240
01:34:24.833 --> 01:34:29.416
<i>No words can express what I feel</i>

1241
01:34:29.500 --> 01:34:36.291
<i>But this much I know</i>

1242
01:34:36.375 --> 01:34:41.416
<i>From your eyes</i>

1243
01:34:41.500 --> 01:34:44.208
<i>I will take away all the darkness</i>

1244
