1260
01:36:11.041 --> 01:36:12.791
<i>Love does not just happen</i>

1261
01:36:13.041 --> 01:36:14.875
<i>To find love this way</i>

1262
01:36:14.958 --> 01:36:17.791
<i>The way I found you</i>

1263
01:36:18.000 --> 01:36:23.125
<i>The cherished life I have with you</i>

1264
01:36:23.250 --> 01:36:26.125
<i>Must be mine forever</i>

1265
01:36:26.208 --> 01:36:29.208
<i>With you. I want nights to be sleepless</i>

1266
01:36:29.291 --> 01:36:30.958
<i>So I can watch you</i>

1267
01:36:31.041 --> 01:36:34.708
<i>Fall into slumber</i>

1268
01:36:34.958 --> 01:36:38.500
<i>With you. everything feels right</i>

1269
01:36:39.125 --> 01:36:42.583
<i>With you. time stands still</i>

1270
01:36:43.041 --> 01:36:47.166
{\an8}<i>With you. this moment is alive</i>

1271
01:36:47.250 --> 01:36:50.750
<i>This moment is eternity</i>

1272
01:36:51.208 --> 01:36:53.833
<i>Because you are here</i>

1273
01:36:58.166 --> 01:36:59.583
<i>Because you are here</i>

1274
01:37:00.083 --> 01:37:02.166
<i>You are here</i>

1275
01:37:02.250 --> 01:37:05.666
<i>There's only you</i>

