1279
01:38:21.791 --> 01:38:24.500
<i>I'm the lead guitarist of Josh.</i>

1280
01:38:24.750 --> 01:38:26.958
<i>And my singing has a massive response.</i>

1281
01:38:27.041 --> 01:38:30.500
<i>When the lead singer</i>
<i>Krish Kapoor shows up.</i>

1282
01:38:30.583 --> 01:38:33.583
