- Krish Kapoor!

1317
01:41:14.833 --> 01:41:16.000
Let's go.

1318
01:41:16.083 --> 01:41:17.166
That's my boy!

1319
01:41:18.416 --> 01:41:20.625
- Let's go.
- Please. sir. One picture.

1320
01:41:20.708 --> 01:41:22.500
Sir. one picture. Sir. please!

1321
01:41:22.583 --> 01:41:24.041
Sir. one picture.

1322
01:41:24.125 --> 01:41:25.375
Don't you forget!

1323
01:41:25.458 --> 01:41:27.541
Guys. you're up next.
Five minutes to cue in.

1324
01:41:27.625 --> 01:41:28.750
Ready.

1325
01:41:28.833 --> 01:41:29.833
No worries. Let's go.

1326
01:41:30.166 --> 01:41:32.166
No worries. Let's go.

1327
01:41:32.250 --> 01:41:33.250
Let's do this.

1328
01:41:35.291 --> 01:41:36.166
I called him.

1329
01:41:36.250 --> 01:41:37.500
RAAG

1330
01:41:40.666 --> 01:41:41.541
Thank you.

1331
01:41:42.708 --> 01:41:43.666
Are you okay?

1332
01:41:46.833 --> 01:41:47.666
What is it?

1333
01:41:50.750 --> 01:41:52.416
I've waited my whole life
for this moment.

1334
01:41:55.291 --> 01:41:56.583
Now it's here. I'm scared.

1335
01:41:59.916 --> 01:42:01.500
Who knows how. and if they'll like me.

1336
01:42:06.083 --> 01:42:07.625
What if they hate me. Vaani?

1337
01:42:08.333 --> 01:42:10.125
It doesn't matter because I love you.

1338
01:42:20.416 --> 01:42:21.791
Josh! Josh!

1339
01:42:21.875 --> 01:42:23.166
No worries. Let's go.

1340
01:42:23.250 --> 01:42:24.083
Go!

1341
01:42:26.416 --> 01:42:28.125
This is my moment. my success.

1342
01:42:28.250 --> 01:42:30.166
I know you're going to kill it for me.

1343
01:42:30.250 --> 01:42:32.208
And I am so. so. so.
so proud of you.

1344
01:42:32.291 --> 01:42:34.416
Don't be scared.
I'll be standing right there.

1345
01:42:34.500 --> 01:42:36.541
Over there. Facing you.

1346
01:42:36.875 --> 01:42:39.208
I'll be watching you.
Cheering for you.

1347
01:42:39.291 --> 01:42:41.875
Makes no difference if they cry out
for you or not.

1348
01:42:41.958 --> 01:42:42.791
Do you know why?

1349
01:42:44.083 --> 01:42:48.250
Because I'll be standing here.
And I'll shout your name the loudest.

1350
01:42:48.333 --> 01:42:50.208
I love you. Krish!

1351
01:42:56.666 --> 01:42:58.041
I still have a few moments left.

1352
01:43:04.083 --> 01:43:06.250
And Josh has a surprise for us.

1353
01:43:06.833 --> 01:43:10.416
The frontman we all know
and loved is back.

1354
01:43:11.333 --> 01:43:15.333
<i>Give a shout out for Krish K…</i>

1355
01:43:26.875 --> 01:43:28.416
Hey guys. thank you so much.

1356
01:43:28.916 --> 01:43:30.125
- Is everything in place?
- Yeah.

1357
01:43:35.791 --> 01:43:36.875
- Keep it inside.
- Yeah.

1358
01:43:44.583 --> 01:43:45.500
Vaani Batra.

1359
01:43:48.875 --> 01:43:49.791
{\an8}Are you stalking me?

1360
01:43:51.625 --> 01:43:52.458
Just kidding.

1361
