Our shows.

1469
01:51:26.000 --> 01:51:27.750
Finished. Cleo. Over.

1470
01:51:28.000 --> 01:51:29.833
Shows over. Josh over.

1471
01:51:30.291 --> 01:51:31.166
Okay?

1472
01:51:42.208 --> 01:51:44.750
You're hesitating
to ask your father for help?

1473
01:51:53.166 --> 01:51:55.875
I made a terrible mistake. son.

1474
01:51:58.166 --> 01:52:00.125
I deserted you.

1475
01:52:04.000 --> 01:52:04.833
Because…

1476
01:52:07.791 --> 01:52:08.791
I couldn't…

1477
01:52:10.416 --> 01:52:11.625
get over your mom.

1478
01:52:13.791 --> 01:52:16.000
Instead of taking care of you…

1479
01:52:18.833 --> 01:52:20.500
I took to the bottle.

1480
01:52:22.250 --> 01:52:24.583
I've just been a failure all my life.

1481
01:52:30.083 --> 01:52:31.750
Let me drop you home. Mr. Kapoor.

1482
01:52:35.083 --> 01:52:37.041
Let me just have…

1483
01:52:37.833 --> 01:52:39.333
Let's meet Vinit tomorrow morning.

1484
01:52:39.541 --> 01:52:40.625
We'll handle it together.

1485
01:52:46.875 --> 01:52:47.791
Sorry.

1486
01:52:50.083 --> 01:52:51.208
But will you take my advice?

1487
01:52:52.916 --> 01:52:55.833
Please never make the mistake
I made in my life.

1488
01:52:57.208 --> 01:52:58.291
In the name of love.

1489
01:53:02.541 --> 01:53:06.458
don't destroy yourself.

1490
01:53:16.208 --> 01:53:17.125
Look after yourself.

1491
01:54:26.583 --> 01:54:27.500
The show…

1492
01:54:31.708 --> 01:54:32.875
Isn't the show on today?

1493
01:54:35.333 --> 01:54:37.791
One second. I'll get ready
and come with you.

1494
01:54:37.875 --> 01:54:39.125
The show was yesterday. Vaani.

1495
01:54:45.166 --> 01:54:46.625
You enjoyed it.

1496
01:54:50.625 --> 01:54:51.500
Oh. yeah!

1497
01:54:53.750 --> 01:54:54.833
I'm so proud of you.

1498
01:54:55.833 --> 01:54:56.750
You were so good.

1499
01:55:13.416 --> 01:55:14.708
Krish. what a lovely song!

1500
01:55:16.750 --> 01:55:18.208
What's your inspiration?

1501
01:55:20.916 --> 01:55:22.791
It's clearly heartfelt.

1502
01:55:29.458 --> 01:55:30.833
I had a friend.

1503
01:55:34.041 --> 01:55:35.166
An old school friend.

1504
01:55:36.583 --> 01:55:38.458
Lost in his own world.

1505
01:55:41.791 --> 01:55:42.666
Anger.

1506
01:55:44.041 --> 01:55:45.083
Frustration.

1507
01:55:48.875 --> 01:55:51.250
Life was too tough on him.

1508
01:56:01.625 --> 01:56:04.333
Then he met a girl.

1509
01:56:06.375 --> 01:56:09.041
Finally. he found something
that he had never had in his life.

1510
01:56:12.333 --> 01:56:13.208
Love.

1511
01:56:16.750 --> 01:56:18.833
He loved for the first time.

1512
01:56:18.916 --> 01:56:21.791
With her by his side. he felt
he could win the world.

1513
01:56:25.791 --> 01:56:29.333
- The problem is she's going away.
- Where?

1514
01:56:31.416 --> 01:56:35.000
Very far. Somewhere. he can't follow her.

1515
01:56:38.208 --> 01:56:41.875
Trust me. he'd leave
the world behind if he could.

1516
01:56:42.833 --> 01:56:45.083
But he can't go to the place
she's going.

1517
01:56:49.291 --> 01:56:51.000
Compose a song for your friend.

1518
01:56:54.541 --> 01:56:55.458
I'll write it.

1519
01:56:58.125 --> 01:56:59.000
And tell him…

1520
01:57:00.500 --> 01:57:03.250
He should tell his girlfriend.
"This one is for you."

1521
01:57:04.958 --> 01:57:05.791
You'll see.

1522
01:57:06.541 --> 01:57:10.375
when the song touches her heart.
she won't leave.

1523
01:57:12.125 --> 01:57:14.500
she'll run back to him.
I promise you.

1524
01:57:19.458 --> 01:57:21.916
Shit! The 9 o'clock ferry.

1525
01:57:23.250 --> 01:57:25.125
Actually. I forgot
I was going to meet KV and Vinit.

1526
01:57:26.333 --> 01:57:27.208
I have to go.

1527
01:57:33.875 --> 01:57:36.000
I still have a few moments left.

1528
01:57:38.541 --> 01:57:39.708
In this moment.

1529
01:57:41.166 --> 01:57:43.541
today. tomorrow.

1530
01:57:44.875 --> 01:57:47.875
forever and ever and ever.

1531
01:57:49.250 --> 01:57:50.791
I love you. Mahesh.

1532
01:58:29.958 --> 01:58:33.791
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1533
01:58:33.875 --> 01:58:37.208
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1534
01:58:37.291 --> 01:58:41.166
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1535
01:58:52.916 --> 01:58:53.833
I'm quitting.

1536
01:58:59.083 --> 01:59:00.291
You guys should go on tour.

1537
01:59:01.166 --> 01:59:02.000
Without me.

1538
01:59:02.625 --> 01:59:03.833
You've worked so hard.

1539
01:59:05.041 --> 01:59:07.708
I'll see you. I'll say sorry to Vinit.

1540
01:59:08.916 --> 01:59:10.291
Hey! Stop!

1541
01:59:10.916 --> 01:59:11.791
You'll say sorry?

1542
01:59:13.875 --> 01:59:15.166
Krish Kapoor? You'll say sorry?

1543
01:59:16.541 --> 01:59:19.000
You made so many mistakes.
abused us

1544
01:59:19.166 --> 01:59:20.375
but never apologized to us.

1545
01:59:22.041 --> 01:59:23.916
- And now…
- KV. KV.

1546
01:59:24.000 --> 01:59:25.166
- Stay out of it!
- KV!

1547
01:59:26.083 --> 01:59:28.208
Boss. I admired you.

1548
01:59:28.833 --> 01:59:31.916
Give me back that selfish.
self-centered friend of mine

1549
01:59:32.000 --> 01:59:34.625
who never let anyone come
in the way of his dreams.

1550
01:59:38.250 --> 01:59:39.083
And…

1551
01:59:40.375 --> 01:59:42.250
Vaani isn't your responsibility.

1552
01:59:43.375 --> 01:59:45.416
Don't take her on. She has parents.

1553
01:59:46.125 --> 01:59:46.958
Let her go.

1554
01:59:49.208 --> 01:59:50.041
Come with us.

1555
01:59:51.291 --> 01:59:54.458
Your dreams and your success
are waiting for you.

1556
01:59:55.708 --> 01:59:58.333
Thousands and thousands
will call out your name.

1557
01:59:58.416 --> 02:00:00.166
They'll shout out!
Krish! Krish! Krish!

1558
02:00:07.541 --> 02:00:08.791
But she won't be there.

1559
02:00:13.583 --> 02:00:16.208
And the world knows my name.
but she can't remember it.

1560
02:00:21.166 --> 02:00:22.208
But I can never forget

1561
02:00:23.833 --> 02:00:25.041
what she's done for me.

1562
02:00:27.916 --> 02:00:29.333
I wanted to be big.

1563
02:00:30.833 --> 02:00:34.291
to be famous. so the world
would love me.

1564
02:00:36.333 --> 02:00:39.000
But she's given me so much love.

1565
02:00:41.250 --> 02:00:42.541
I don't need anything else.

1566
02:00:44.916 --> 02:00:46.250
I cannot leave her.

1567
02:00:47.958 --> 02:00:50.208
I want to live in her world.

1568
02:00:56.041 --> 02:00:57.750
I can't follow you to that world.

1569
02:00:59.375 --> 02:01:00.208
Sorry.

1570
02:01:03.125 --> 02:01:04.041
Let's go.

1571
02:01:36.583 --> 02:01:37.458
Vaani.

1572
02:01:44.750 --> 02:01:45.583
Vaani.

1573
02:01:48.791 --> 02:01:49.666
Vaani.

1574
02:01:52.208 --> 02:01:53.083
Vaani!

1575
02:02:12.916 --> 02:02:13.750
Vaani!

1576
02:02:17.333 --> 02:02:18.416
ALIBAUG POLICE

1577
02:02:25.500 --> 02:02:26.625
She's an adult.

1578
02:02:27.958 --> 02:02:29.541
Was there any fight at home?

1579
02:02:31.333 --> 02:02:33.208
What crime are you reporting?

1580
02:02:36.666 --> 02:02:37.958
She has Alzheimer's. Sir.

1581
02:02:38.833 --> 02:02:40.541
Why didn't you keep an eye on her?

1582
02:02:41.625 --> 02:02:42.583
How could you let her go alone?

1583
02:02:56.541 --> 02:02:58.833
- Please. can you…
- She's in our system now.

1584
02:02:58.916 --> 02:03:00.375
All police stations
are looking for her.

1585
02:03:01.166 --> 02:03:03.708
Let's wait. When we hear anything.
we'll let you know.

1586
02:03:04.208 --> 02:03:06.958
I've been following her case
for the last two months.

1587
02:03:07.541 --> 02:03:08.875
It isn't that simple.

1588
02:03:09.791 --> 02:03:13.125
You will find that there are
350.000 missing persons.

1589
02:03:13.958 --> 02:03:15.041
We'll try our best.

1590
02:03:15.625 --> 02:03:18.583
To be honest. the chances
of finding her are slim…

1591
02:03:49.791 --> 02:03:50.625
Krish.

1592
02:03:52.541 --> 02:03:53.416
Come.

1593
02:04:19.833 --> 02:04:20.708
I love you.

1594
02:04:20.791 --> 02:04:22.791
I love you. I love you.

1595
02:04:24.041 --> 02:04:27.250
I love you. I love you.
I love you.

1596
02:04:37.791 --> 02:04:38.916
I love you. Forever.

1597
02:05:03.250 --> 02:05:05.000
{\an8}<i>Compose a song for your friend.</i>

1598
02:05:06.125 --> 02:05:07.041
{\an8}<i>I'll write it.</i>

1599
02:05:08.375 --> 02:05:12.208
{\an8}<i>When the song touches her heart.</i>
<i>she won't leave…</i>

1600
02:05:12.291 --> 02:05:13.916
{\an8}SAIYAARA

1601
02:05:14.083 --> 02:05:16.500
…and she'll run back to him.
I promise you.

1602
02:05:30.916 --> 02:05:31.791
KV.

1603
02:05:32.166 --> 02:05:33.041
Krish.

1604
02:05:48.583 --> 02:05:49.500
What are you doing. Krish?

1605
02:05:50.583 --> 02:05:52.916
I'm going to give you the biggest
song of my life. KV.

1606
02:05:54.583 --> 02:05:56.083
Promise me. In every house.

1607
02:05:56.625 --> 02:05:58.500
in every lane. everywhere.
this song will be heard.

1608
02:05:58.583 --> 02:05:59.875
That's the only way
it'll reach Vaani.

1609
02:06:01.916 --> 02:06:02.958
I don't know where she is.

1610
02:06:04.000 --> 02:06:06.041
Wherever she is. she must
hear this song.

1611
02:06:08.958 --> 02:06:10.583
Promise me. you'll make the song big.

1612
02:06:14.458 --> 02:06:15.333
Promise me. KV.

1613
02:06:16.666 --> 02:06:17.625
Stop it. Krish.

1614
02:06:19.000 --> 02:06:21.708
Vaani isn't in any condition to hear
or understand your song.

1615
02:06:27.250 --> 02:06:28.125
This is her diary.

1616
02:06:31.333 --> 02:06:32.666
She was the one who told me about it.

1617
02:06:34.833 --> 02:06:36.166
Told me that no one could
forget this song.

1618
02:06:38.458 --> 02:06:39.833
She wrote the words.

1619
02:06:43.125 --> 02:06:45.875
I know the song will touch her
and she'll come back to me.

1620
02:06:51.000 --> 02:06:52.083
I'll find her. KV.

1621
02:06:55.458 --> 02:06:56.375
I know I will.

1622
02:06:58.375 --> 02:07:03.208
{\an8}SAIYAARA

1623
02:07:12.333 --> 02:07:15.250
{\an8}Krish K. Krish K.

1624
