<i>- You're so close to me. so close</i>
- Krish!

1627
02:07:59.125 --> 02:08:04.916
<i>Like a feeling within me</i>

1628
02:08:05.000 --> 02:08:10.125
<i>You're so close to me. so close</i>

1629
02:08:10.750 --> 02:08:15.958
<i>Like an emotion I've always known</i>

1630
02:08:16.416 --> 02:08:18.750
<i>I will not survive</i>

1631
02:08:19.416 --> 02:08:21.666
<i>If you're not with me</i>

1632
02:08:22.333 --> 02:08:25.458
<i>Lost in the thoughts of your words</i>

1633
02:08:25.583 --> 02:08:27.875
<i>I spend all my nights</i>

1634
