<i>Only time has turned its back on us</i>

1642
02:09:50.375 --> 02:09:55.500
<i>Let me create a world</i>
<i>Of sweet moments lived together</i>

1643
02:09:56.250 --> 02:10:01.833
<i>I was made from your falling tears</i>

1644
02:10:01.916 --> 02:10:07.208
<i>In my smile. your voice sings</i>

1645
02:10:07.708 --> 02:10:13.000
<i>I tell myself stories of you</i>

1646
02:10:13.500 --> 02:10:16.416
<i>The memories of stars never fade</i>

1647
02:10:25.166 --> 02:10:30.833
<i>How can the memory of stars ever fade?</i>

1648
02:10:30.916 --> 02:10:36.583
<i>How can my arms ever be lonely?</i>

1649
02:10:36.666 --> 02:10:42.416
<i>Those books of our days together</i>

1650
02:10:42.500 --> 02:10:48.041
<i>How can I forget those precious pages?</i>

1651
