<i>Only time has turned its back on us</i>

1663
02:11:48.583 --> 02:11:51.291
<i>The sensational Indian musician. Krish K</i>

1664
02:11:51.375 --> 02:11:53.708
{\an8}<i>along with his electrifying band Josh…</i>

1665
02:11:53.875 --> 02:11:55.750
{\an8}<i>has just landed in London.</i>

1666
02:11:56.000 --> 02:11:59.375
{\an8}<i>The biggest show performed by</i>
<i>any Indian at Wembley.</i>

1667
02:11:59.458 --> 02:12:02.541
<i>they are all set to bring their</i>
<i>unstoppable energy and</i>

1668
02:12:02.625 --> 02:12:04.833
<i>unforgettable soundtracks to…</i>

1669
02:12:16.833 --> 02:12:18.500
Josh! Josh!

1670
02:12:18.583 --> 02:12:21.041
- Josh! Josh!
- Wembley. baby!

1671
02:12:22.666 --> 02:12:25.916
- Mic one check. one check.
- Guys. let's run the sequence again.

1672
02:12:26.166 --> 02:12:28.625
Our songs are attracting the most Reels!

1673
02:12:28.791 --> 02:12:31.541
We're the most reeled artists in India!

1674
02:12:31.625 --> 02:12:33.541
And top ten in the world!

1675
02:12:33.625 --> 02:12:34.708
This is insane!

1676
02:12:35.125 --> 02:12:36.666
Can we have this
on the big screen. please?

1677
02:12:36.750 --> 02:12:37.875
- Okay.
- Thank you.

1678
02:12:40.541 --> 02:12:41.916
Mic delay check.

1679
02:12:43.125 --> 02:12:44.541
This is a disgrace. bro.

1680
02:12:45.750 --> 02:12:47.666
India has a population of 1.5 billion.

1681
02:12:47.958 --> 02:12:50.208
Why isn't our song number one?

1682
02:12:51.125 --> 02:12:55.625
Vinit Sir. announce a prize
of a million for the best Reel.

1683
02:12:55.708 --> 02:12:57.500
Yeah. yeah. I'll do it.

1684
02:12:58.000 --> 02:13:00.875
Vinit Sir will announce it.
but he won't pay up.

1685
02:13:05.666 --> 02:13:07.958
This is straight from Himachal.

1686
02:13:16.333 --> 02:13:17.875
Pause. pause. pause.

1687
02:13:23.333 --> 02:13:24.833
- This is to zoom. right?
- Yeah.

1688
02:13:58.333 --> 02:14:02.208
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1689
02:14:02.291 --> 02:14:05.625
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1690
02:14:05.708 --> 02:14:08.791
<i>Saiyaara!</i>

1691
02:14:13.375 --> 02:14:15.958
I've spoken to that influencer.
and the video is from Manali.

1692
02:14:16.166 --> 02:14:17.708
I found a local contact in Manali.

1693
02:14:17.791 --> 02:14:21.083
I'll book you a chartered flight.
I'll also inform her parents.

1694
02:14:28.833 --> 02:14:31.958
Krish. where are you going?
Our biggest show is in three days.

1695
02:14:32.125 --> 02:14:34.916
No Indian has had as big a show here.

1696
02:14:37.041 --> 02:14:40.000
Krish! If you don't do this show.
you're finished.

1697
02:14:41.958 --> 02:14:42.833
Krish!

1698
02:15:15.291 --> 02:15:18.875
{\an8}SHAKTI WOMEN'S SHELTER

1699
02:15:23.291 --> 02:15:24.541
Hurry up!

1700
02:15:25.833 --> 02:15:26.750
Over here.

1701
02:15:26.833 --> 02:15:27.791
Krish Kapoor?

1702
02:15:30.958 --> 02:15:32.375
We didn't think you'd come here.

1703
02:15:34.750 --> 02:15:36.666
She only used to talk about you.

1704
02:15:37.541 --> 02:15:40.000
We assumed she was
a big fan of yours.

1705
02:15:41.208 --> 02:15:44.333
Then a few weeks ago.
she handed me this.

1706
02:15:45.416 --> 02:15:49.708
She asked me to give you this
in case you come here.

1707
02:15:54.875 --> 02:15:57.916
{\an8}<i>Krish. I hope you never get this letter.</i>

1708
02:15:59.666 --> 02:16:01.750
<i>If you're reading this letter. it means…</i>

1709
02:16:02.458 --> 02:16:05.833
<i>that you've left everything behind.</i>
<i>and came in search of me.</i>

1710
02:16:07.250 --> 02:16:08.416
<i>I didn't want that.</i>

1711
02:16:11.541 --> 02:16:15.625
<i>You gave me everything. and you're</i>
<i>giving up everything. I didn't want it.</i>

1712
02:16:17.583 --> 02:16:19.541
<i>To my colorless life.</i>

1713
02:16:20.875 --> 02:16:22.500
<i>you brought color. Krish.</i>

1714
02:16:24.416 --> 02:16:25.250
<i>And then.</i>

1715
02:16:26.041 --> 02:16:30.125
<i>I realized there was something</i>
<i>that was changing inside me.</i>

1716
02:16:31.750 --> 02:16:33.500
It's my moment. it's my success.

1717
02:16:33.583 --> 02:16:36.125
And I know that you're
going to kill it for me.

1718
02:16:36.208 --> 02:16:37.375
I'm so. so. so…

1719
02:16:37.458 --> 02:16:38.625
So proud of you.

1720
02:16:41.666 --> 02:16:43.041
<i>It's a strange disease. Krish.</i>

1721
02:16:43.416 --> 02:16:45.000
Let him go! I love him.

1722
02:16:45.541 --> 02:16:47.708
<i>When I can't remember much.</i>
<i>I hurt others.</i>

1723
02:16:48.875 --> 02:16:50.041
<i>When I remember things.</i>

1724
02:16:51.000 --> 02:16:52.125
<i>it hurts me.</i>

1725
02:16:57.291 --> 02:16:58.916
I love you. Mahesh.

1726
02:17:02.000 --> 02:17:02.916
<i>It pains me a lot.</i>

1727
02:17:03.625 --> 02:17:06.083
{\an8}SAIYAARA

1728
02:17:07.833 --> 02:17:09.000
{\an8}<i>That's why I ran away.</i>

1729
02:17:11.333 --> 02:17:12.208
From you.

1730
02:17:13.541 --> 02:17:14.375
<i>From everyone.</i>

1731
02:17:17.041 --> 02:17:19.250
<i>My greatest regret is</i>
<i>not being with you.</i>

1732
02:17:20.958 --> 02:17:24.875
<i>Like. in person.</i>
<i>and I'm so sorry about that.</i>

1733
02:17:26.500 --> 02:17:32.083
<i>But I knew my absence would be</i>
<i>the reason for your success.</i>

1734
02:17:33.708 --> 02:17:34.625
<i>And see.</i>

1735
02:17:35.791 --> 02:17:37.000
<i>you got there!</i>

1736
02:17:39.583 --> 02:17:41.416
<i>I remember so little these days.</i>

1737
02:17:42.541 --> 02:17:44.208
